    "Bulent Eczacibasi and brother Faruk are partners in a conglomerate that includes a building products company with 13 facilities in Turkey and Europe.",
    "It is a global exporter of ceramic and wall tiles, plus bathroom fixtures and accessories (brands include VitrA, Villeroy & Boch and Engers Keramik).",
    "Bulent's father, Dr. Nejat F. Eczacibasi, focused on pharmaceuticals before expanding into personal health care and other businesses.",
    "Eczacibasi Holding also operates in healthcare services and the production and distribution of medical products to hospitals.",
    "Other key sectors are consumer products, finance, IT, mining and real estate development. Eczacibasi is Turkey's leading producer of toilet paper."
